===============================================================================
PROHIBITED USE
===============================================================================

The following uses are absolutely prohibited. Engaging in any Prohibited Use
immediately and irrevocably terminates all rights granted under this license,
without notice, without cure period, and without any obligation on the part
of the Licensor to provide remedy.

No commercial license, payment, or agreement of any kind can unlock or
permit these uses. They are not restrictions that dissolve upon payment.
They are the floor below which this Software will not go.

  1. SURVEILLANCE
     The Software may not be used to monitor, track, or collect data on
     individuals without their meaningful, informed, and freely given
     consent. This includes but is not limited to: covert device tracking,
     behavioral profiling without disclosure, and mass collection of
     communications content.

  2. WEAPONS
     The Software may not be used in the development, operation, guidance,
     targeting, or deployment of weapons systems of any kind. This includes
     autonomous weapons, drone targeting, missile guidance, cyberweapons
     designed to cause physical harm, and any military application in which
     this Software contributes to the harm or death of persons.

  3. OPPRESSION
     The Software may not be used to suppress political dissent, restrict
     freedom of expression, or identify, target, or harm individuals on
     the basis of their beliefs, ethnicity, religion, sexuality, gender
     identity, or political views. This includes building or operating
     infrastructure that enforces laws criminalizing identity or belief.

  4. MANIPULATION
     The Software may not be used to build systems designed to manipulate
     human behavior, belief, or decision-making at scale without disclosure.
     This includes algorithmic radicalization systems, coordinated
     inauthentic behavior infrastructure, and mass psychological
     manipulation platforms.

  5. AI TRAINING EXTRACTION
     Works created using the Software, and the Software itself, may not be
     used as training data for commercial AI systems without the explicit
     written permission of the human creator of those works. Automated
     collection, scraping, or ingestion for AI training purposes without
     such permission is a violation of this license regardless of its
     technical form or the publicly accessible nature of the content.

  6. SECRET GOVERNMENT COMPLIANCE
     No entity distributing the Software may comply with any government
     order that requires modification of the Software in ways that weaken
     its security, privacy, or integrity guarantees, without publicly
     disclosing the existence of such an order to the maximum extent
     permitted by applicable law. If such disclosure is legally prevented,
     the entity must cease distribution of the Software rather than
     distribute a version whose compromise cannot be disclosed.

